		<div>Had to register here just because of this post and the others in this forum!  Fantastic read and thanks to all the beta testers who have taken the time to answer questions, post pictures and give information.  I am eagerly waiting to play WoW, it looks like a lot of fun!  I played EQ for several years, but I am done playing that now for various reasons and I am really looking forward to WoW more than ever.  Anyway, it was great for me to get a perspective on the game from people who have played EQ.<br />
<br />
I have one question, and I know not everything is done being balanced yet of course, but right now for grouping, do people worry about having X class and pass up people who want to group based on class?  This was a huge problem for me in EQ (my main was a druid, don't hate me :p ) and I am hopeful that it won't be in WoW, whatever class I pick.  All the classes sound so much fun, though I am most interested in shaman and warlock atm.  Thanks again!</div>
