		<hr />
		
		
		
		
		<div>I'm not in the beta (*cries*), but from what I've read I think it works something like this:  <br />
<br />
Some items (like the head of Big Mr. X) are special quest items, and enough of that item will drop for everyone in the group.  Other items (like a fire beetle leg) are just normal drops from creatures that you've been asked to gather for a quest.  These gathering quests do not count the drop as special quest items, so they only drop at whatever frequency is set for the game.  <br />
<br />
Hopefully someone from beta can confirm or set me straight.  :)</div>
	</td>
</tr>
</table>
