				<div style="font-style:italic">Some items (like the head of Big Mr. X) are special quest items, and enough of that item will drop for everyone in the group.  Other items (like a fire beetle leg) are just normal drops from creatures that you've been asked to gather for a quest.  These gathering quests do not count the drop as special quest items, so they only drop at whatever frequency is set for the game.</div>
			
			<hr />
